  Rod donned a powder blue polka-dotted shirt, accessorising with a white beaded necklace and matching bracelets. He paired the shirt with some cream chinos, a white fedora and some white trainers. The star carried a shopping bag in one hand and a white umbrella in the other as he browsed. Former model Penny looked sensational in a pink, floral printed mini dress, which she paired with some light pink shades. She wore her hair in a glamorous up-do and carried a large orange tote bag as well as a colourful Fendi bag on each shoulder.   